{"tid":525260,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我們的愛 過了就不再回來","createTime":"2018-01-10T12:29:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-14T10:05:20.000Z","uid":36377,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"de57f1f1058a9fae94b35e26b80f1febb085bb23","tid":525260,"uid":36377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T12:29:17.000Z","msg":"直到現在我還默默的等待<br />\n我們的愛　我明白　已變成你的負擔<br />\n只是永遠　我都放不開　<br />\n最後的溫暖　你給的溫暖<br />\n<br />\n從此以後我都不敢抬頭看　<br />\n彷彿我的天空失去了顏色<br />\n從那一天起　我忘記了呼吸　<br />\n眼淚啊永遠不再　不再哭泣<br />\n<br />\n由個一日開始，變返自己一個人<br />\n回到自己最習慣也是最不習慣的生活<br />\n而這一個月我都開始在感情台長駐起來<br />\n看見一個又一個的同路人<br />\n在此祝各位失落、空虛、翻滾在煎熬的巴絲們<br />\n早日走出傷痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n瞓唔著就係到傾計啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ba270e04e062995e6b4e341c108857dede2c1db","tid":525260,"uid":165024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T12:30:27.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d5cb174c94cf7c7c5938a85c17b29689b429c74","tid":525260,"uid":89680,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T12:31:14.000Z","msg":"咁早就講瞓唔著"},{"pid":"faf757bb4a2149aa0dc58c96d3c7048284da8c67","tid":525260,"uid":137361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T12:32:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dfe52f0997ca10372edfe7527e0c623c7acc5f24","tid":525260,"uid":36377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T12:32:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁早就講瞓唔著</blockquote><br />\n成個月都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開定先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"865d77fb8c454f4fdd4a9fea1d914dda244c38fa","tid":525260,"uid":36377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T12:33:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁早就講瞓唔著</blockquote>我仲睇睇時間 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n順便咋嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b34f35aac5180f836f8457b9bf68ec8c21c0280","tid":525260,"uid":165024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T12:33:28.000Z","msg":"好凍<br />\n<br />\n準備冬眠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a541c646ce49807aaea79d3c2c16ff3dfb6864b2","tid":525260,"uid":70429,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T12:33:48.000Z","msg":"唔講以為5p交友網"},{"pid":"7b8ff93df86da1f6e2561f3235cb9c148492e720","tid":525260,"uid":36377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T12:34:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好凍<br />\n<br />\n準備冬眠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n瞓得著就瞓啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n執靚靚好重新上路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f0ce893cd767ceed333e2fff0f29dba5a350637","tid":525260,"uid":157596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T13:51:13.000Z","msg":"幾個月都係咁 但叫做開始瞓得翻覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57c9143672bdbf959832c8620ca6b9d0b251ba6f","tid":525260,"uid":89494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T14:07:26.000Z","msg":"好頹"},{"pid":"9a20b3f76abe13953a58f11f84ccc16cf4a54175","tid":525260,"uid":165024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T14:10:48.000Z","msg":"上水啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96835d253e88f68fe446b68d89ec7235029f525f","tid":525260,"uid":36377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T15:29:30.